I know about her!\", \"from\": 194, \"to\": 212, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She's competing in her fourth Olympics.\", \"from\": 213, \"to\": 252, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her fourth Olympics\", \"from\": 232, \"to\": 251}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I watched a documentary about her, I admire her.\", \"from\": 253, \"to\": 301, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a documentary\", \"from\": 263, \"to\": 276}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a privilege to shoot against her, unfortunately I lost.\", \"from\": 302, \"to\": 364, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a privilege\", \"from\": 309, \"to\": 320}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Deepika Kumari, the object of the young Quinty's awe, grins happily when she learns the kid she beat is her fan - it's not every day that your opponent watches a documentary about you before competing against you at the Olympics.Quinty, unfortunately, crumbled under pressure after beginning strongly - she had a 9, 9, 10 in the first set, but Deepika won the set and two points for it by hitting bullseye twice - 10, 10, 9.Quinty then turned the tables - 10, 10, 9 against Deepika's 9, 9, 9; the rookie had tightened the screws on the veteran, the score was tied 2-2.Quinty, sensing an opportunity against the fabled Kumari, could not control the throbbing of her heart.\", \"from\": 364, \"to\": 1036, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 983, \"end\": 989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raja_Kumari\", \"score\": 0.9754325691635851, \"rank\": 0.025186190837876016, \"text\": \"Kumari\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raja_Kumari\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raja_Kumari\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Deepika Kumari\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 379}, {\"ngram\": \"the object\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 391}, {\"ngram\": \"the young Quinty's awe\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 417}, {\"ngram\"